channel.title: Comments on: Epic Day of Tetris… I Mean… Go…

item.title: By: Todd
item.dc:creator: Todd
item.description: Congratulations on the epic win! All four corners! It'll take a while to beat that high score. Try practicing rotating pieces in both directions rather than ever turning a piece three times, it makes a big difference!
